body:
### Welcome to TeraCore's Website.
This will not be our website for long it is just a backup untill our main website is completed. You can check out the new branch:

```
### ## # **[TeraCore](https://github.com/terabyte101/TeraCore)**
```

### We are working hard and we need you!
The Team has been working hard and we need some developers to help out and make a few pull requests.
Please try to help us out as much as you can.

### Authors and Contributors
At the momment its just me (Terabyte) that is working on the core. As i said above please make some pull requests.

### Support or Contact
If you need to report a bug just report in the Issues section located : [ISSUES](https://github.com/terabyte101/TeraCore/issues)
